{"tid":170833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡少年余澎杉獲美國庇護","createTime":"2017-03-25T02:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-25T05:01:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c20b4a4c9140fd04bdbd15bbc1953808f7377f8b","tid":170833,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:43:49.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】曾批評新加坡已故總理李光耀的少年博客余澎杉獲得美國庇護。<br />\n<br />\n芝加哥移民法官科爾頒下十三頁判詞，指十八歲的余澎杉成功證明自己因為政治立場被迫害，因此可以繼續留在美國。<br />\n<br />\n余澎杉去年十二月抵達芝加哥後申請庇護，被移民當局扣留至今，預料他最快會在周一獲釋。<br />\n<br />\n他的律師表示，余澎杉對判決感到非常高興，余澎杉曾多次在網絡發表敏感言論，包括辱罵已故新加坡總理李光耀，以及批評新加坡政府自稱民主社會，但所作所為，有如北韓前領導人金正日。<br />\n<br />\n他的行為令他曾經兩度在新加坡入獄。他在芝加哥申請庇護時曾表示，對回去新加坡感到害怕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=215361\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D215361&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=0e5bc959\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D215361&h=0f23b72d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=215361</a>"},{"pid":"b60a47762eb0b9d11e0eaf82b1c2a8434d61ec81","tid":170833,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e2a5f89de2c83202f29cbb42b353db8a8e41ed","tid":170833,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:53:21.000Z","msg":"會唔會即刻有人批評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de81c093f085fa14355d794e544546274ea19d65","tid":170833,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-25T02:57:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會即刻有人批評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n坡仔實嬲到震"},{"pid":"ffc317613dcc68e6af198ff0d3be58fd364a6116","tid":170833,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike"